      <hedline>
        <hl1>Introduction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Summary of major topic of letters, on Jan 6 article about Arctic research of George Divoky2</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Readers were riveted by our cover article on George Divoky's Arctic bird-watching, research that he is conducting to support a theory of global warming. Many were impressed by the importance of his work (those birds tell a big story) -- and equally inspired by his dedication.</p>
      </block>
